{"tid":2190423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国信用體系進階版  再推「文明碼」　積分太低將懲戒","createTime":"2020-09-05T15:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T17:01:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"060efb6068317b95675832fc265fe845f4b6aab0","tid":2190423,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"繼「健康碼」後，中國江蘇省蘇州市近期結合社會信用體系，推出「蘇城文明碼」，宣稱積分越高者在各種生活領域均能享有優先便利，機制還將用於「警示和懲戒文明指數低於下限人員」。<br />\n<br />\n這項作法再度引發議論，有中國網友質疑，文明無法以分數量化，「根本是『黑鏡』真實版」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=809565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D809565&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=eb23331c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D809565&h=5d26ed73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=809565</a>"},{"pid":"84be423e19c5dacb0ece2eec481ee52a746ec566","tid":2190423,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負分唔俾出街"},{"pid":"d9b7a597bfbc2b40a69526aad71367de242e3be2","tid":2190423,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84be423e19c5dacb0ece2eec481ee52a746ec566","tid":2190423,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負分唔俾出街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"人工絕育<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e129f47461903e0298ca7355dc94f09ce317de","tid":2190423,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"black mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif